header.title: Combtech
header.subtitle: Website development and presentation branding elaboration.

text: Focused on producing 3D printers with low costs, Combtech is a startup founded in 2015 in the Incubator of the Federal Technological University of Paraná (UTFPR, in portuguese). In order to expand its recognition and to return the knowledge acquired to the university academic students, the company asked to develop a website for its main course and redesign the company’s presentations in 2017.
Tech stack: Photoshop, Powerpoint, PHP, Materialize CSS, jQuery.
